# K-LINE MEN — Netlify redirect rules
# Docs: https://docs.netlify.com/routing/redirects/

# Old PDP URL form (?id=…) → clean pre-rendered URL.
# Search-engine friendly 301 so any indexed query-string URLs migrate cleanly.
/product.html  /product/:id  301  id=:id

# Trailing-slash variant → canonical .html file
/product/:id/  /product/:id.html  301
